  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Trim the green stalk<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> off the<strong> aubergine<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and cut into bite-sized pieces, discard the stalk<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>aubergine</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and put the tray in the oven and cook for 15-18 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2427Step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
